hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Have you seen any good films recently? prostaglandin uterine contraction The Global offices, which also house the more youth-orientated likes of Capital and XFM, are full of bright lights, loud music and funky soft furnishings, ensuring that Nick Clegg, as he strides down the corridors in a stuffy suit, looks like a deeply uncool member of the legal department nipping off for a loo break. But once he’s shut in the studio for his weekly Call Clegg phone-in, with his small entourage of interchangeable minions waiting outside the door like particularly weedy bouncers, he seems more at home, loudly greeting Ferrari like an old friend, even remembering to ask him about his bad back.
